data.description: Here is the opportunity to acquire a great property in highly demanded Bristol Park, 11411 Stella Way. Including 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, you are going to enjoy the 2,384 sqft that composes this House built in 2018. Nested in an enjoyable neighborhood, and minutes from local attractions, public transportation, and public parks. Don't miss this great opportunity This house features, open floor plan, formal office/dining room. New stainless steel smart refrigerator, new stainless steel microwave, new smart oven/cooktop, new garbage disposal. Granite counters throughout the house. Brick exterior, newer pool, and whole yard sprinkler system. Back yard fully fenced.
